              the <bibl sameAs="ed_etf_mhf_lbb">Commonwealth</bibl>.</orig><note xml:id="f053fe8f-b72f-44aa-9892-6df357b50f05"><bibl sameAs="zotero-604880-4RFNUY45" type="primary">Ernest Jones: To the editor of the Commonwealth.</bibl> In: The
              Commonwealth. London. Nr. 163, 21. April 1866. S. 5.
              <!--(((lJones, Ernest: To the editor of the
                            Commonwealth. In: The Commonwealth. London. Nr. 163, 21. April
                            1866. S. 5.)))--></note></seg></p><p sameAs="MBTextmitEinzug">Will you kindly give it to <seg type="comment"><orig>the
                            Editor,</orig><note xml:id="f60011df-a057-4753-9566-c369da6432b1"><persName key="pdrPo.001.004.000003494">George Odger</persName>.
                        </note></seg> whose address I have not got.</p><p sameAs="MBTextmitEinzug">I hope it will go in</p><p sameAs="MBTextmitEinzug">Kind regards at home.</p><p sameAs="MBTextmitEinzug">I wish I was with <pb/> you away from this pig-stye.</p><p sameAs="MBTextmitEinzug">Kindest regards at home,</p><closer sameAs="MBUnterschrift">Ever yours<lb/>Ernest Jones. </closer></div></body></text></TEI>